161
00:10:10,500 --> 00:10:13,050
Stop complaining, Wolf!

162
00:10:13,050 --> 00:10:16,170
The raft was almost broken because of you.

163
00:10:16,170 --> 00:10:18,510
That's why we're doing this.

164
00:10:18,510 --> 00:10:24,640
It was so reckless to try crossing the
New World by raft in the first place.

165
00:10:24,810 --> 00:10:29,900
