175
00:10:44,240 --> 00:10:46,180
Shut up or I'll kill you.

176
00:10:46,180 --> 00:10:48,210
We're Blackbeard Pirates.

177
00:10:48,210 --> 00:10:53,540
Heaven knows what'll happen to us... Oh...

178
