183
00:11:02,660 --> 00:11:06,590
Yeah, I'd prefer some
gorgeous outfit to a ship!

184
00:11:06,590 --> 00:11:08,600
I'm sick of this jail clothing.

185
00:11:08,600 --> 00:11:10,850
You have to live with it.

186
00:11:10,850 --> 00:11:13,730
I can't live with it forever.

187
00:11:13,730 --> 00:11:17,280
Me, neither! How much longer should we wait?!

188
00:11:17,640 --> 00:11:20,070
Is the Navy coming?

189
00:11:20,110 --> 00:11:23,660
VAN AUGER

190
00:11:20,450 --> 00:11:24,120
I'll go and look. They can't be this slow.

191
00:11:24,520 --> 00:11:25,880
No, they can't!

192
00:11:25,730 --> 00:11:28,910
These guys are getting tired of waiting.

193
00:11:32,340 --> 00:11:35,920
Right, Jewelry Bonney?

194
00:11:33,540 --> 00:11:38,510
JEWELRY BONNEY

195
00:11:36,040 --> 00:11:37,620
Captain Bonney...

196
00:11:42,400 --> 00:11:47,470
I can't believe they put a price of
over 100 million on a girl like you!

197
00:11:48,030 --> 00:11:51,390
The New World is the sea
for the chosen strong ones.

198
00:11:51,390 --> 00:11:54,900
Although you came all the
way from the South Blue,

199
00:11:54,900 --> 00:11:57,720
you can't go any further.

200
00:12:02,420 --> 00:12:05,700
You're too weak to join my crew but...

201
00:12:05,700 --> 00:12:10,000
How about this? You can come
with me if you become my girl.

202
00:12:11,330 --> 00:12:14,250
To go further. Huh?

203
00:12:14,810 --> 00:12:16,670
Screw you!

204
00:12:16,670 --> 00:12:18,210
You bearded pig!

205
00:12:20,090 --> 00:12:21,990
He got turned down.

206
00:12:22,720 --> 00:12:27,220
No good! You're indecent! Women
need to have some decency!

207
00:12:27,220 --> 00:12:30,520
