225
00:13:33,830 --> 00:13:35,040
Disappeared?

226
00:13:35,040 --> 00:13:38,250
Yeah, to be honest.

227
00:13:39,060 --> 00:13:42,590
Whose idea was this?! Sengoku?!

228
00:13:42,960 --> 00:13:46,630
No, someone much higher up the ladder!

229
00:13:49,470 --> 00:13:54,020
It's not a metaphor. Literally,
it was like "poof."

230
00:13:54,940 --> 00:13:59,100
I was surprised. Is that the
power of the Shadow-Shadow Fruit?

231
00:13:59,100 --> 00:14:00,690
It's no joke!

232
00:14:00,690 --> 00:14:05,240
Don't worry. He was dying.

233
00:14:05,240 --> 00:14:07,530
Nothing can save his life.

234
00:14:07,530 --> 00:14:11,840
