see you again, Racoon!

250
00:15:29,570 --> 00:15:33,150
Now, let's get back to work.

251
00:15:41,280 --> 00:15:43,460
Ah? What is it?

252
00:15:44,060 --> 00:15:45,610
That's...!

253
00:15:45,610 --> 00:15:49,130
--The bird came back!
--Huh? It's too soon!

254
00:15:51,300 --> 00:15:55,720
--Oh? I don't see Racoon.
--What happened to Racoon?

255
00:15:55,720 --> 00:16:02,020
--Maybe he fell into the water!
--That's not good! Let's go look for...

256
00:16:05,060 --> 00:16:07,110
Wh-Who is it?

257
00:16:07,400 --> 00:16:13,170
As a matter of fact, in order
to defend peace in the world,

258
00:16:13,170 --> 00:16:18,660
