hero of justice - Chopper Mask!

259
00:16:22,540 --> 00:16:24,870
Ra-Racoon!

260
00:16:24,870 --> 00:16:29,050
I know I said "come see us again"
but isn't it a little bit too soon?

261
00:16:29,050 --> 00:16:31,680
No, you're wrong! I'm not him!

262
00:16:31,680 --> 00:16:35,840
Maybe we look alike but I'm
his friend--Chopper Mask!

263
00:16:35,840 --> 00:16:38,010
It's too obvious, Racoon.

264
00:16:38,010 --> 00:16:42,020
You're wearing a disguise because
you feel embarrassed to come back?

265
00:16:42,020 --> 00:16:44,560
No! I said I'm...

266
00:16:48,360 --> 00:16:50,780
Are you okay, Racoon?

267
00:16:50,780 --> 00:16:53,450
Don't make me repeat myself!
I'm his friend and I'm...

268
00:16:53,450 --> 00:16:57,450
You guys, don't be such jerks.

269
00:16:57,450 --> 00:17:00,370
You gotta play along on these occasions.

270
00:17:00,700 --> 00:17:04,580
--We got confused!
--Yeah, that's right!

271
00:17:04,580 --> 00:17:10,380
--So you're Chopper Mask! Cool!
--Yeah, you don't look anything like Chopper!

272
00:17:10,380 --> 00:17:12,710
Sorry, sorry, we were...

273
00:17:12,710 --> 00:17:15,010
That's enough! It's too pitiful!

274
00:17:15,420 --> 00:17:17,340
Oh, Racoon!

275
00:17:25,430 --> 00:17:28,400
That tickles! You fool!

276
00:17:33,490 --> 00:17:37,190
The thing is, I suddenly have something that
I need to do.

277
00:17:37,190 --> 00:17:38,920
Can I stay a little longer?

278
00:17:38,920 --> 00:17:42,330
Whatever the reason, you're always welcome!

279
00:17:43,040 --> 00:17:45,070
There are many plants

280
00:17:45,070 --> 00:17:48,770
that I've never seen in any
book growing on that big tree.

281
00:17:48,770 --> 00:17:50,960
Let me study them.

282
00:17:51,600 --> 00:17:54,460
Then we have a suitable place for that.

283
00:17:55,090 --> 00:17:58,030
I need to improve my strength, too.

284
00:17:58,030 --> 00:17:59,510
I have a lot to do.

285
00:18:00,190 --> 00:18:03,350
Oh, Racoon! You're back already?

286
00:18:03,350 --> 00:18:04,890
That's great!

287
00:18:04,890 --> 00:18:09,480
You guys, I'm gonna stay
on this island for a while!

288
00:18:09,860 --> 00:18:12,070
Okay, this is it.

289
00:18:13,030 --> 00:18:14,920
What's this place?

290
00:18:14,920 --> 00:18:16,240
This is...

291
00:18:26,120 --> 00:18:30,520
...the library of our
village. You can study here.

292
00:18:30,520 --> 00:18:32,640
So many books!

293
00:18:33,880 --> 00:18:36,630
There are more! To the very end!

294
00:18:38,420 --> 00:18:39,950
Cool!

295
00:18:39,950 --> 00:18:44,470
All these books are about the plants
and the medicines that I wanna study!

296
00:18:44,810 --> 00:18:47,310
And there're so many!

297
00:18:47,310 --> 00:18:50,770
There are so many plants on this island
that you can make medicine out of.

298
00:18:51,540 --> 00:18:55,590
And we knew how to make them
but the birds were in our way

299
00:18:55,590 --> 00:18:59,740
so we couldn't get the plants and
make medicine - we were stuck.

300
00:19:00,070 --> 00:19:03,620
I was judging the people on
this island by their looks

301
00:19:03,950 --> 00:19:07,580
but when I think about it, their
weapons are very high-tech.

302
00:19:07,910 --> 00:19:10,830
They look like they're dumb but...

303
00:19:10,830 --> 00:19:14,710
...their cultural level is pretty high!

304
00:19:14,710 --> 00:19:16,130
I have a lot to learn!

305
00:19:16,130 --> 00:19:17,630
Racoon!

306
00:19:17,630 --> 00:19:22,140
You thought you were saying that to
yourself, but you actually said it.

307
00:19:22,140 --> 00:19:24,030
And that was very rude...

308
00:19:24,030 --> 00:19:28,250
I wonder how much I can do in this country...

309
00:19:30,060 --> 00:19:32,190
Hey, what's that thing?!

310
00:19:32,520 --> 00:19:34,150
It must be the Snowman!

311
00:19:34,150 --> 00:19:37,870
It's dangerous! Tell the
kids to get in the house.

312
00:19:37,870 --> 00:19:39,610
Gun! Bring me the gun!

313
00:19:40,610 --> 00:19:43,620
Kill it! Go away, monster!

314
00:19:43,620 --> 00:19:46,280
Don't let it come any closer! Kill it now!

315
00:19:48,810 --> 00:19:51,400
--It's the Snowman!
--Kill it!

316
00:19:51,400 --> 00:19:53,760
--Don't let it get away!
--Kill it!

317
00:20:12,370 --> 00:20:13,350
Skull?

318
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:18,730
This is a symbol of the belief
that nothing is impossible.

319
00:20:18,730 --> 00:20:22,530
By raising this, I'll fight
just like pirates do!

320
00:20:22,530 --> 00:20:24,700
It's cool to be a pirate!

321
00:20:24,700 --> 00:20:27,870
There're tons of incredible guys at sea!

322
00:20:27,870 --> 00:20:30,700
Chopper, go out to sea some day.

323
00:20:30,700 --> 00:20:35,120
If you do, you'll understand very
well how small your problems are.

324
00:20:35,120 --> 00:20:40,210
This island you were born on is
like this compared to the world.

325
00:20:40,210 --> 00:20:41,260
Really?

326
00:20:41,260 --> 00:20:44,880
No, it's smaller! Like this! It's true!

327
00:20:47,850 --> 00:20:51,770
Your future lies beyond that sea!

328
00:20:53,430 --> 00:20:57,730
Hey! Let's be pirates together!

329
00:20:57,730 --> 00:21:01,490
It's true... that I wanna be a pirate but...

330
00:21:03,740 --> 00:21:07,700
I'm not even a human! I'm a monster!

331
00:21:07,700 --> 00:21:11,760
I can't become your friend! So...!

332
00:21:12,540 --> 00:21:14,380
So I just came to say thank you...

333
00:21:17,670 --> 00:21:19,900
I do appreciate you guys.

334
00:21:20,460 --> 00:21:22,550
Thank you for asking me to join you.

335
00:21:24,010 --> 00:21:26,170
I'll stay here, but...

336
00:21:27,550 --> 00:21:30,360
one day... if you feel
like it, stop by agai...

337
00:21:30,360 --> 00:21:34,800
Shut up! Let's go!

338
00:21:46,920 --> 00:21:49,350
Luffy took me out to sea.

339
00:21:50,160 --> 00:21:52,200
I was desperate to just follow him.

340
00:21:53,310 --> 00:21:55,200
Have I done anything to help Luffy?

341
00:22:01,540 --> 00:22:05,510
I don't wanna go through that again.

342
00:22:06,860 --> 00:22:09,550
But, at that time...

343
00:22:27,500 --> 00:22:31,990
Luffy must have felt more
pain than the rest of us!

344
00:22:35,120 --> 00:22:37,880
Because he let me join his crew,

345
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:41,380
I no longer care what people say to me!

346
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:50,040
If it helps him,

347
00:22:51,850 --> 00:22:55,180
I can become a real monster!

348
00:22:55,770 --> 00:22:57,230
Chopper!

349
00:22:57,820 --> 00:22:59,140
Chopper!

350
00:22:59,850 --> 00:23:01,500
Chopper!

351
00:23:09,080 --> 00:23:12,120
Luffy!

352
00:23:12,120 --> 00:23:18,150
I promise you that I'm gonna get stronger!

353
00:23:25,530 --> 00:23:27,700
Luffy's friends have received his messages.

354
00:23:27,700 --> 00:23:28,970
Nami, in Weatheria,

355
00:23:28,970 --> 00:23:32,680
and Franky, in Baldimore, take
action in their own ways.

356
00:23:32,680 --> 00:23:35,140
And Sanji, in Kamabakka Kingdom,

357
00:23:35,140 --> 00:23:39,810
throws his all into an epic battle to learn a
secret handed down in the kingdom for generations!

358
00:23:39,810 --> 00:23:41,350
On the next episode of One Piece!

359
00:23:41,350 --> 00:23:44,730
"Living through Hell! Sanji's
Fight for His Manhood!"

360
00:23:44,730 --> 00:23:47,290
I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
